data.description: Welcome to your dream home nestled on a picturesque pond lot! This immaculate 2-story residence boasts comfort, style, and entertainment options galore. With 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and a wealth of upgrades, this property offers the ideal setting for your family's next chapter. The entire home features beautiful laminate flooring, creating a cohesive and easy-to-maintain living environment. It adds an elegant touch while being practical for daily living. The heart of the home is the well-appointed kitchen, featuring upgraded cabinets and a spacious pantry. Prepare meals with ease, entertain guests, and enjoy the convenience of modern amenities with this open floor plan.Enjoy the convenience of a spacious owner's suite located on the ground floor. This private retreat offers a tray ceiling, walk-in closets and a serene pond view, providing the perfect backdrop for relaxation.  Upstairs, discover a huge loft that will become your family's entertainment hub. Complete with a projector and screen, it's the ultimate space for movie nights, gaming sessions, or even a home office. Unleash your creativity and make this space your own.  Step out onto your screened-in porch and extended patio, overlooking the stunning pond. This outdoor oasis is ideal for morning coffee, evening sunsets, and year-round enjoyment. Host gatherings with ease in this tranquil setting.  This property is more than a home; it's a lifestyle upgrade. With its combination of practicality, comfort, and entertainment options, it's a perfect match for families looking to make lasting memories.  Don't miss out on this opportunity to make this stunning 2-story home your own. Schedule a viewing today and experience the magic of all Cane Bay has to offer!  Old Rice Retreat at Cane Bay Plantation, a resort-style masterplan community designed for every family type. Located in Summerville, SC, residents enjoy luxurious community amenities such as a beautiful swimming pool, nature trails and scenic lakes, along with access to the new YMCA that features a 54,000-square-foot sports facility. From front porches and friendly neighbors to hiking trails and parks to play in, Old Rice Retreat is like no other community. As an added perk, this beautiful home is zoned for the highly sought after Cane Bay Elementary, Middle, and High Schools. Don't miss out!
